{"thig6.6:0.1":"Therigatha 6.6 ","thig6.6:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.6:0.3":"Mahapajapatigotamitherigatha ","thig6.6:1.1":"“Buddha vira namo tyatthu, ","thig6.6:1.2":"sabbasattanamuttama; ","thig6.6:1.3":"Yo mam dukkha pamocesi, ","thig6.6:1.4":"annanca bahukam janam. ","thig6.6:2.1":"Sabbadukkham parinnatam, ","thig6.6:2.2":"Hetutanha visosita; ","thig6.6:2.3":"Bhavito atthangiko maggo, ","thig6.6:2.4":"Nirodho phusito maya. ","thig6.6:3.1":"Mata putto pita bhata, ","thig6.6:3.2":"ayyaka ca pure ahum; ","thig6.6:3.3":"Yathabhuccamajananti, ","thig6.6:3.4":"samsarimham anibbisam. ","thig6.6:4.1":"Dittho hi me so bhagava, ","thig6.6:4.2":"antimoyam samussayo; ","thig6.6:4.3":"Vikkhino jatisamsaro, ","thig6.6:4.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thig6.6:5.1":"Araddhaviriye pahitatte, ","thig6.6:5.2":"Niccam dalhaparakkame; ","thig6.6:5.3":"Samagge savake passe, ","thig6.6:5.4":"Esa buddhana vandana. ","thig6.6:6.1":"Bahunam vata atthaya, ","thig6.6:6.2":"Maya janayi gotamam; ","thig6.6:6.3":"Byadhimaranatunnanam, ","thig6.6:6.4":"Dukkhakkhandham byapanudi”ti. ","thig6.6:7.1":"… Mahapajapatigotami theri …. "}